{
  "stem": "1550.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So the first 200 people packed their bags, and they went down on a big barge, and they went over to the-- to the Patria.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went over, then the barge came back empty, and picked up the second 200, and they left for the Patria.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They left for the Patria, but we couldn't really see the Patria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could see only the three funnels at the other side of the port.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then suddenly, those three funnels disappeared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were just gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't hear any sound or explosion or anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But what happened then, afterwards, the last group of people who had been transshipped, or were supposed to be, they came back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were all crying and said the ship has capsized, and there are all people swimming in the water, and terrible things are happening, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we knew that something terrible had happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened next was that the British decided, well, we couldn't stay onboard the ship, they're going to-- to send us to a camp after all.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were taken off the ship, and my father and I went to a camp-- like a detention camp or whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A camp with barracks in Acre.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother, for one reason or another, went to a ladies' camp-- a women camp in Atlit, which is just outside of-- of Haifa, if you know the place.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there we stayed for about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there we recovered some.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- we had comparatively good food and we were able to take showers and all of that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had breakfast and lunch and dinner, which I'm sure it was very plain, but it was very good.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably British Army food, I would assume.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
